Moon Extension Features:

1. Every new tab displays a shuffled Moon wallpaper.
2. Customize your background from the Moon wallpaper selection panel or set favorites.
3. Integrated Google search bar.
4. Direct links to your email and social media platforms.
5. Automatically displays the current date and time.
6. Note feature for jotting down important tasks.
7. Quick links to frequently visited websites.
8. Convenient bookmark access.
9. Shortcut panel for adding and accessing favorite sites quickly.
10. Immediate access to Google applications.
11. Explore more themes with ease.
12. Simplified social media sharing.
13. Download wallpapers directly from the new tab.
14. Instant access to gaming.
15. Activate engaging animations like snow, rain, falling leaves, and fireworks on your new Moon tab.
